OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has appointed John Healey
OL,8,Fas Chancellor as he announces his
OL,9,Ffirst cabinet after becoming prime
OL,10,Fminister on Monday.
OL,12,FThe appointment is unexpected, after
OL,13,Fmuch speculation pointing to Shabana
OL,14,FMahmood and Ed Miliband as
OL,15,Ffrontrunners for the job ` both of
OL,16,Fwhom were seen walking up Downing
OL,17,FStreet together to meet the UK's new
OL,18,FPM.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
