FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FMahmood will remain in position as
OL,8,Fhome secretary, while Miliband will
OL,9,Fmove from his post as Energy Secretary
OL,10,Fto become the Foreign Secretary.
OL,12,FHealey has experience in the Treasury,
OL,13,Ffrom his time as Economic Secretary to
OL,14,Fthe Treasury and Financial Secretary
OL,15,Fto the Treasury under Tony Blair and
OL,16,FGordon Brown's governments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
