FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the prime minister
OL,8,Fsaid he wants the economy to work
OL,9,Fbetter for working people and says
OL,10,Fthat Burnham and Healey share the same
OL,11,Foutlook.
OL,13,FThey also credited Healey's experience
OL,14,Fas a housing minister, suggesting it
OL,15,Fcould prove useful for Burnham's
OL,16,Fplanned delivery of council homes.
OL,18,FPat McFadden will remain in his role
OL,19,Fof Work and Pensions Secretary while
OL,20,Fformer Foreign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,21,Fmoves over to become Health Secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
