OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FSince the 2024 election, McFadden has
OL,8,Fserved as Chancellor of the Duchy of
OL,9,FLancaster before moving to work and
OL,10,Fpensions, with Cooper taking on Home
OL,11,FSecretary before reshuffle by Keir
OL,12,FStarmer saw her move to the Foreign
OL,13,FOffice.
OL,15,FLouise Haigh, seen as Burnham's right
OL,16,Fhand woman, has been given the role of
OL,17,FFirst Secretary of State, Chancellor
OL,18,Fof the Duchy of Lancaster, and
OL,19,FMinister for the Cabinet Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
