FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FThe First Secretary of State is a role
OL,8,Fgiven to a closest aide or ally, held
OL,9,Fin previous governments by figures
OL,10,Flike George Osborne and John Prescott.
OL,12,FAngela Rayner is set to return to
OL,13,Fcabinet as she was spotted walking
OL,14,Finto No 10 on Monday evening.
OL,16,FShe was cleared of any wrong doing by
OL,17,FHMRC following a row over stamp duty
OL,18,Fwhen she was housing secretary under
OL,19,FSir Keir Starmer, an upset which led
OL,20,Fto her resignation in September 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
