PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FLisa Nandy, Jonathan Reynolds, Bridget
OL,8,FPhillipson and Lucy Powell have also
OL,9,Fentered Downing Street but their
OL,10,Fpositions are yet to be confirmed.
OL,12,FThe announcement comes after Burnham
OL,13,Fwas officially appointed prime
OL,14,Fminister by the King on Monday.
OL,16,FSpeaking from Downing Street in front
OL,17,Fof a crowd of political allies, the
OL,18,Fnew PM pledged to "help people to live
OL,19,Fwell" and said he will announce
OL,20,Fproposals to tackle the cost-of-living
OL,21,Fon Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
