OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FHis cabinet will be tasked with
OL,8,Fdelivering on Burnham's plan.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FSeveral former cabinet ministers have
OL,16,Fconfirmed they will not be returning
OL,17,Fto cabinet under Burnham's leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
