OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FRachel Reeves is out Chancellor,
OL,8,Fsaying "the economy today is stronger,
OL,9,Ffairer and more resilient" because of
OL,10,Fher work.
OL,12,FThe first ever woman to take on the
OL,13,Frole running the nations' finances,
OL,14,FReeves said: "to every young woman and
OL,15,Fgirl let my time in office show there
OL,16,Fshould be no ceilings on your
OL,17,Fambitions, your hopes or your dreams."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
