CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784665115
OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FFormer Deputy prime minister and
OL,8,FJustice secretary David Lammy posted
OL,9,Fon social media to say it "has been
OL,10,Fthe greatest privilege of my life" to
OL,11,Fserve in government and said he
OL,12,Fwould've been "proud to continue
OL,13,Fserving in Cabinet".
OL,15,FA staunch ally of Starmer, it is not
OL,16,Fsurprising that Lammy will not return
OL,17,Fand he acknowledge that "a new prime
OL,18,Fminister is entitled to build his own
OL,19,Fteam" and wished them success.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
