OL,3,CJohn Healey made Chancellor and Ed
OL,4,CMiliband Foreign Secretary in Burnham
OL,5,Ccabinet
OL,7,FFormer Housing Secretary Steve Reed
OL,8,Fposted a letter on X to confirm his
OL,9,Fdeparture.
OL,11,FIn a scathing line he said "I hope
OL,12,Fthose who did not show loyalty to Keir
OL,13,Fwill now show it to you" as he
OL,14,Fexpressed his pride in his own
OL,15,Fintegrity "over the turbulent past few
OL,16,Fmonths".
OL,18,FConfirmed Departures:
OL,20,FThis is a breaking news story. More to
OL,21,Ffollow
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
